{{! The licenses workflow wraps this output in its own document header and     }}
{{! section banners, so this template starts straight at the content.          }}
{{!                                                                            }}
{{! Every field is written with a triple stache. This renders a plain text     }}
{{! file, and the double stache form escapes for HTML, which turns the quotes  }}
{{! in a licence into &quot; and stops it being the verbatim text the licence  }}
{{! requires us to reproduce.                                                  }}
{{!                                                                            }}
{{! Field reference, since the names are not guessable:                        }}
{{!   overview[]  - one entry per distinct license: id, name, count.           }}
{{!                 It has no version and no crate, so do not try to list      }}
{{!                 components from here.                                      }}
{{!   licenses[]  - one entry per license text: id, name, text, used_by.       }}
{{!                 The same license appears more than once when crates ship   }}
{{!                 it with different copyright lines, so used_by is the only  }}
{{!                 place the component names live.                            }}
SUMMARY
-------

{{#each overview}}
{{{name}}}: {{{count}}} crate(s)
{{/each}}

================================================================================
COMPONENTS AND THEIR LICENSES
================================================================================

{{#each licenses}}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{{{name}}}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Used by:
{{#each used_by}}
  - {{{crate.name}}} {{{crate.version}}}
{{/each}}

{{{text}}}

{{/each}}
